<div type="definition">
<p>BODY JUICE ISSUED FROM the BODY WHEN it is HOT, OR WHEN IT USES MUCH STRENGTH.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current word for sweat is hàn 汗.</p>
<p>2. Cí 泚 is a rare word for sweat, probably a dialect word, which happens to be used by Mencius.</p></div>
